api_list.description:
This API endpoint provides a basic list of dog parks and dog beaches within a specified radius of up to 5 kilometers from a given reference coordinate. It allows users to retrieve information about nearby areas, enabling them to plan activities and outings with their canine companions. The endpoint returns a basic list of details for each entry, like next example:

"center_coord": {
                "type": "Point",
                "coordinates": [
                    41.364865,
                    2.09479355
                ]
            },
            "_id": "6226318f1dd149a77c27c1d9",
            "properties": {
                "@id": "way/929266172",
                "area": "yes",
                "leisure": "dog_park"
            },
            "type": "Feature",
            "feature_id": "way/929266172",
            "__v": 0,
            "credits": "Pipican.app"
}
